data.title: Orthopedic, Sports Medicine and Spine Physicians
data.meta_description: Our orthopaedic doctors are experts in adult and pediatric orthopaedics care from neck to toe. Schedule with Chicago's top orthopaedic surgeons for bone, joint, spine and sports medicine care.
data.text:
We have your back.

At Duly Health and Care, we are here for you. Our team under­stands that bone, joint, and spine injuries have a phys­i­cal and men­tal­ impact, and that recov­ery takes time.

We will part­ner with you on your health and care jour­ney, and meet you wher­ev­er you are, to devel­op a spe­cif­ic treat­ment plan for your unique needs. Our tight-knit team of spe­cial­ists will make sure you have the most com­plete med­ical, reha­bil­i­ta­tive, diag­nos­tic and sur­gi­cal meth­ods pos­si­ble. Our goal is for you to reach your extra­or­di­nary health potential…because at Duly Health and Care, we believe that health­i­er makes happier.

Bone Health Clinic

If you are 50 and old­er, and have expe­ri­enced a fragili­ty frac­ture, we may refer you to the Duly Health and Care Bone Health Clin­ic, for­mer­ly known as Frac­ture Liai­son Ser­vice. Learn more about man­ag­ing your risk for future frac­tures here.

Work­ers’ Compensation

If you have a recent­ly suf­fered a work-relat­ed injury, we can pro­vide treat­ment options for your Work­ers’ Com­pen­sa­tion claim or pro­vide an Inde­pen­dent Med­ical Eval­u­a­tion here.
